<br>
Examples of things in Guild now (not implying that the people with these items would consider selling them).<br>
<br>
Jaundiced Breastplate = 5 points<br>
valued between 40-70k<br>
A 5 point return of this item once a Shaman got a better item would be worth not selling.<br>
a 2.5 point return instead of selling for around 50k is questionable at best<br>
<br>
Sheild of Rainbow Hues = 1 point<br>
valued between 20-30k<br>
a 1 point return would be a debatable issue on this, where as a .5 point return would be unthinkable, it would probably be sold.<br>
<br>
Defiance = .5 points<br>
Valued between 15-20k<br>
Even returning this for the full.5 point value would be a bad deal, alot more could be bought with 15k than can be gained with .5 points, not to mention even thinking about .25 points<br>
